    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so if the main value is just having a place to talk, does that mean the UN is essentially just a tool for the powerful to keep things the way they are? like, is the \"diplomatic forum\" argument actually a legitimate defense of the institution, or is it just an excuse to avoid making the fundamental changes needed to make it actually work?",
